Package: causalworkshop
Title: Educational Package for Causal Inference with Machine Learning
Version: 0.1.5
Authors@R: 
    person("Joseph", "Bulbulia", , "joseph.bulbulia@vuw.ac.nz", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5861-2056"))
Description: Provides educational tools and workflows for learning causal inference 
    using machine learning methods, particularly causal forests. Includes simulation 
    functions, analysis workflows, and comprehensive tutorials for understanding 
    heterogeneous treatment effects, policy learning, and targeting analysis.
